definition.message:
Percentage of interface utilization to identify high traffic levels relative to the interface capacity.

{{#is_alert}}
{{snmp_device.name}} in namespace {{device_namespace.name}} is reporting high bandwidth utilization (at or over 90%) sent on interface {{interface.name}}
{{/is_alert}}

{{#is_warning}}
{{snmp_device.name}} in namespace {{device_namespace.name}} is reporting high bandwidth utilization (at or over 80%) sent on interface {{interface.name}}
{{/is_warning}} 

{{#is_recovery}}
Device {{snmp_device.name}} in namespace {{device_namespace.name}} has interface {{interface.name}} with bandwidth usage for outgoing traffic in normal range.
{{/is_recovery}}
